"title": "4909: beginning",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4909: beginning",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A starting point, origin or source. The beginning often refers to the time of or before the creation of the world. God is described as the Beginning and the End, denoting the eternity of his existence. Jesus Christ's coming marks a new beginning both for God's people and, finally, for all creation.</p>\n<h2>Beginning as the starting point</h2>\n<h3>As the source</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps111:10\">PSA 111:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:7\">PRO 1:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:10\">PRO 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:13\">MIC 1:13</a> <em>the source of Israel's sin</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18\">COL 1:18</a> <em>Jesus Christ as the source of the church's life</em></p>\n<h3>As the origin</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:7\">JOB 8:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:4\">ACT 26:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:3\">HEB 7:3</a></p>\n<h3>As the commencement</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev23:5\">LEV 23:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:19\">JDG 7:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:1\">1KI 6:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:1\">2CH 3:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:54\">LUK 23:54</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:7\">1JN 2:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:5\">2JN 1:5</a></p>\n<h2>The beginning: before the creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:22-Prov8:23\">PRO 8:22–8:23</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's existence predates the creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:5\">JHN 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:1-John1:2\">JHN 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:58\">JHN 8:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:17\">COL 1:15–1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1\">1JN 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:13-1John2:14\">1JN 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Salvation planned before the creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:4\">EPH 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:7\">1CO 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:13\">2TH 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:9\">2TI 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:2\">TIT 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>The beginning: the creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:10\">HEB 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:25\">PSA 102:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:21\">ISA 40:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:1\">DAN 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:21\">MAT 24:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:19\">MRK 13:19</a></p>\n<h3>Marriage ordained from the beginning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:4-Matt19:6\">MAT 19:4–19:6</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:6-Mark10:9\">MRK 10:6–10:9</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:27\">GEN 1:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a></p>\n<h2>The beginning of Israel's nationhood</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:2\">EXO 12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:10\">2SA 7:10</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:9\">1CH 17:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:4\">ISA 52:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:2-Jer2:3\">JER 2:2–2:3</a></p>\n<h2>New beginnings for God's people</h2>\n<h3>For Israel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos2:14-Hos2:15\">HOS 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:26\">ISA 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:18-Isa43:19\">ISA 43:18–43:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:26\">ISA 44:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:4\">ISA 61:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:7-Jer33:9\">JER 33:7–33:9</a></p>\n<h3>For believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2CO 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:6\">2CO 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:10\">EPH 2:10</a></p>\n<h3>A new creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">ISA 66:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:1\">REV 21:1</a></p>\n<h2>Beginnings of significant events</h2>\n<h3>The rebuilding of Jerusalem</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:18\">NEH 2:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:14\">HAG 1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's ministry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:17\">MAT 4:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:1\">MRK 1:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:15\">MRK 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:23\">LUK 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:1\">ACT 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>The beginning of signs of the end</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:7-Matt24:8\">MAT 24:7–24:8</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:8\">MRK 13:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:28\">LUK 21:28</a></p>\n<h2>The beginning and the end</h2>\n<h3>Implying all-inclusiveness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen44:12\">GEN 44:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:24\">DEU 31:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:12\">1SA 3:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:8\">MAT 20:8</a></p>\n<h3>The beginning and end contrasted</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:21\">PRO 20:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:8\">ECC 7:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:20\">2PE 2:20</a></p>\n<h3>Completing what is begun</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:6\">2CO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:3\">GAL 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:14\">HEB 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:5\">REV 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:19\">REV 2:19</a></p>\n<h3>God as the Beginning and the End</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:6\">ISA 44:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:6\">REV 21:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa41:4\">ISA 41:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:12\">ISA 48:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:17\">REV 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:8\">REV 2:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:13\">REV 22:13</a></p>\n<h2>Satan as sinful from the beginning</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:44\">JHN 8:44</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:8\">1JN 3:8</a></p>",
